    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">As one who is very particularly concerned, may I pay my respect to the Minister for his bigness in going back on his original policy, and may I express my gratification that he has adopted this course which will help so many of us who have lost limbs?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
